  "description": "Specify mixed models using ASReml-style or brms-style formula syntax and estimate them via greta (Bayesian MCMC), INLA (integrated nested Laplace approximation), or brms (Stan passthrough). Returns results in formats compatible with the standard R modelling ecosystem, with cross-engine posterior triangulation exposed as a first-class robustness diagnostic.",
